{"tid":1644264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【應網友要求2】2019年香港自殺資料統計(跳落死亡)","createTime":"2019-10-10T13:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T23:12:28.000Z","uid":4273,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"87f955b9b202bf2bbdc62247377bc564da0582c7","tid":1644264,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"大家好 又係我 2019年香港自殺資料統計 嘅作者<br />\n<br />\n噚日發佈咗<br />\n【應網友要求】2019年香港自殺資料統計(淹溺死亡)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1642123/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1642123/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n再有網友想了解 墮樓(跳落)死亡嘅個案<br />\n咁我抽起咗 2019年 <span style=\"color: red;\">跳落死亡(或屍體發現)</span> 嘅數據<br />\n大家可以透過以下試算表嘅分析參考一下<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aYyuUIXIq3bnk-AsQvf6zgmqu74aMa87lwbbImf41gY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1aYyuUIXIq3bnk-AsQvf6zgmqu74aMa87lwbbImf41gY%2F&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=655ea743\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1aYyuUIXIq3bnk-AsQvf6zgmqu74aMa87lwbbImf41gY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2hrs2Jh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2hrs2Jh.jpg&h=c0f376f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZgD9ow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZgD9ow.jpg&h=c2ec5fb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b5384a5b29a7364eedc8153d0cd0d684eafc260","tid":1644264,"uid":4273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:22:54.000Z","msg":"// 統計數據從來只會反映整體的客觀事實，並不會成為任何論述的助燃劑。除了實質證據能告訴我們事實真相，其他數字都只能作為一般參考。 //<br />\n<br />\n【2019年香港自殺資料計】<br />\n本文件旨在記錄香港每日由新聞報導之自殺數據，以便用作討論。<br />\n本文件並非鼓吹自殺行為，請珍惜生命，關心身邊家人及朋友。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=297287f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideHTML&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=8a5e87e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideAPI&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=c44d1df6\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideCleanDATA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideCleanDATA&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=5943cff7\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideCleanDATA</a>"},{"pid":"daab385c70052c3f36c42152c053a055ee79180e","tid":1644264,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"【Share過雲呑博士篇〈殺人警察〉嘅同我入嚟，炒晒車喇你哋！】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/uawoi/posts/2457428351012829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fuawoi%2Fposts%2F2457428351012829&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=67507fa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/uawoi/posts/2457428351012829</a><br />\n<br />\n撮要：<br />\n0. 大家都想知真相，但想知就唔應該畀流料阻住我哋，下面再解釋，睇完先講，唔好留廢話。<br />\n<br />\n1. 雲呑博士用嘅資料錯到離晒譜，佢都明顯無睇清楚自己引用嘅資料。<br />\n<br />\n2. 有人話畀佢知數據有錯，佢話任何人都可以有自己嘅詮釋，仲拋錯書包咁話「作者已死」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 佢掛博士個名岀嚟，文中強調學術，用錯數據誤導大眾，而且篇文廣傳（FB 18K share，連登熱門post），有錯唔認唔可以姑息。<br />\n<br />\n4. 唔好以為質疑警察、可以令大家關注831事件就無問題，錯誤資訊對整個運動有害無益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/uawoi/posts/2457428351012829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fuawoi%2Fposts%2F2457428351012829&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=67507fa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/uawoi/posts/2457428351012829</a>"},{"pid":"06a30efbb830695a71800e77819074977c6d0915","tid":1644264,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"【應網友要求】2019年香港自殺資料統計(淹溺死亡)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1642123/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1642123/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5152f292bbbe4b13b34f3a8817b33b839efeb483","tid":1644264,"uid":60547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:36:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cc83c22721172f0da66b85d7a26fe6a418b155f2","tid":1644264,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T13:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a8854ecc67c861ea0e5b67cce1fd0376168ec8","tid":1644264,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085541914e0b79e2c05fbc3da601e950941cb4c4","tid":1644264,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c3d845910883428ba8f0f7c8db5a89deca03bc6","tid":1644264,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b891fcacbc412d48a2296fbddb2ee930e928d9b","tid":1644264,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:02:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f2956d7a19adb12886a60e003240d974b67bcad","tid":1644264,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:02:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58f6a57dd69dcc15d2b56d2225bf569f6f9a55d2","tid":1644264,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:02:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e01881720008772817ecf8cf3306c18ce22fb20","tid":1644264,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":